description: Demolition of the existing building, redevelopment and construction of a new building on three basement levels, ground, and part four/part seven floors comprising 60 flats (Class C3), a health & fitness club (Class D2) ), a retail shop (Class A1), a restaurant or public house (Class A3/A4), storage uses (Class B8),  replacement accommodation for street cleansing facilities (sui generis), car parking for the development and 23 parking spaces for local residents, associated plant.
